				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$E = \frac{{hc}}{\lambda }$$\end{document}). This equation is used to convert between efficiency and efficacy, and it is used to calculate the maximum possible photosynthetic photon efficacy for a given spectrum.
